main event: A woman reported a UFO sighting involving an uncontrolled red blinking light traveling at an altitude of up to 30,000 feet.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately 5 minutes., The UFO was reported to the Navy., The sighting occurred on August 31, 1960., A radar tape record of the target was mentioned., The UFO was noted to be traveling northeast at 1,000 feet altitude.
witness description: a woman who reported the UFO
